  <brief_title>Habitual Abortion Study: Oral Dydrogesterone Treatment During Pregnancy in Women With Recurrent Miscarriage</brief_title>
  <official_title>Oral Dydrogesterone Treatment During the First Trimester of Pregnancy in Women With Recurrent Miscarriage: A Double-Blind, Prospectively Randomized, Placebo-Controlled, Parallel Group Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
