  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this clinical study is to demonstrate the shift from inflammatory cytokines to
      non-inflammatory cytokines in women suffering from habitual abortion treated with
      dydrogesterone (Duphaston).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
